MESSAGE.value: Started implementing the auto property -> propertyType. Need to test it.

Tested the auto property -> propertyType. It is running. Almost complete. About to start reimplementing the attribute generation, e.g. domain count, range count, same type possible, etc. Next sep will be to map (propType, attributes) -> strategies DECISIONS: I am rewriting all queries to use SPARQL raw, instead of my old solution generating the queries, it looks much nicer and produce fewer errors.

Tested the auto property -> propertyType. Note prevously |ItemProperites| > |ItemProperties| now, I need to check why this is the case... Attribute generation, e.g. domain count, range count, same type possible, etc. and mapping to strategies are done. It is running now. Going forward I would like to use a webserver to interact with the application. This would help me understand the application better. But first I need to do some refactoring.

ARCHITECTURE REFACTORING. Summarized: 1. The SimpleRDF abstraction is removed. 2. Folder structure are changed to accomodate for both similarity finder and structure finder. A core package contains all the common logic. 3. Old unused files, or files using the (1) abstraction is removed.

Prioritize testing. ActiveTag for tests that are pretty fast and should be run every time. TestOnlyTag when doing one test at a time. Changed GraphRDF to have multiple types. Next: Finish the property to strategy mapping for Wikidata.
Implicit knowledge graph must be specified when executing queries to allow both Wikidata and DBpedia...
